                    "ECB reveals patterns in plaintext because identical blocks encrypt identically.", DifficultyLevel.INTERMEDIATE),
                QuizQuestion("cq4", "What is the main advantage of ECC over RSA at equivalent security levels?",
                    ["ECC is older and more tested", "Smaller key sizes and faster computation", "ECC cannot be broken", "ECC is simpler to implement"], 1,
                    "ECC achieves equivalent security with much smaller keys (e.g., 256-bit ECC ~ 3072-bit RSA).", DifficultyLevel.INTERMEDIATE),
                QuizQuestion("cq5", "Which password hashing algorithm won the Password Hashing Competition?",
                    ["bcrypt", "scrypt", "Argon2", "PBKDF2"], 2,
