                    "PFS uses ephemeral key exchange so past sessions cannot be decrypted later.", DifficultyLevel.ADVANCED),
                QuizQuestion("cq7", "In TLS 1.3, which key exchange mechanism is preferred?",
                    ["RSA key transport", "Ephemeral Diffie-Hellman", "Static DH", "Pre-shared keys only"], 1,
                    "TLS 1.3 mandates ephemeral key exchange (DHE or ECDHE) for forward secrecy.", DifficultyLevel.ADVANCED),
                QuizQuestion("cq8", "What is the purpose of a Certificate Authority (CA)?",
